<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>404 ERROR</title>
    <style>
      .notFound {
        width: 200px;
        height: 200px;
        display: block;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        margin-top: 5vh;
      }
      .notFoundhome {
        display: block;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        width: 300px;
        height: 40px;
        border: 1px solid aliceblue;
        background-color: aliceblue;
        border-radius: 10px;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: slateblue;
        cursor: pointer;
      }
      .errtitle {
        text-align: center;
      }
      .errsub {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: normal;
        white-space: pre-line;
      }
      /* 모바일 */
      @media screen and (max-width: 500px) {
        .notFound {
          width: 100px;
          height: 100px;
          margin-top: 5vh;
        }
        .notFoundhome {
          width: 150px;
          font-size: 14px;
        }
        .errtitle {
          font-size: 20px;
        }
        .errsub {
          font-size: 10px;
        }
      }

      /* 테블릿 */
      @media screen and (max-width: 800px) {
        .notFound {
          width: 200px;
          height: 200px;
        }
        .notFoundhome {
          width: 200px;
          font-size: 16px;
        }
        .errtitle {
          font-size: 24px;
        }
        .errsub {
          font-size: 14px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div>
      <img
        class="notFound"
        src="https://kdt8-cs.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8%ED%95%98%EC%B9%B4_icon/ExclamationTriangleFill.svg"
        alt="404 error"
      />
      <br />
      <h1 class="errtitle">오류가 발생했습니다</h1>
      <h2 class="errsub">
        주소가 잘못 입력되거나 변경 혹은 삭제되어 페이지를 찾을 수 없어요
      </h2>
      <br />
      <button class="notFoundhome" onclick="home()">홈으로 이동</button>
    </div>
    <script>
      function home() {
        location.href = "/";
      }
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
